Monday March 27 Mehlemamba renews the hunt for Mpiyakhe. Zama s condition does not seem to be getting better. Tuesday March 28 Mpiyakhe manages to get comfort in an unlikely place. Zama is very weak and the doctors and Jabu fear the worst. Wednesday March 29 While Mehlemamba fears the worst over Mpiyakhe, there s a desperate last attempt to save Zama s life. Thursday March 30 Mehlemamba returns to the hills and his worst suspicions are confirmed. Meanwhile, Jabu waits anxiously for news on Zama. Friday March 31 A body has washed up on the bank of the river. Beauty fears that she might have lost her daughter forever.